Like Katy Perry's
at the LCA tonight,

00:10:15.370 --> 00:10:17.203
so we're planning to
have a pretty big night

00:10:17.203 --> 00:10:18.970
and some good commerce downtown.

00:10:18.970 --> 00:10:22.650
So you had also
mentioned originally

00:10:22.650 --> 00:10:25.580
about the second floor.

00:10:25.580 --> 00:10:27.530
You know, if you're
on the first floor

00:10:27.530 --> 00:10:31.160
of a building in a storefront,
you see cars and people.

