On the second floor, if you
look out Wright Company,

00:10:33.784 --> 00:10:35.200
or if you're in
table 40-- we call

00:10:35.200 --> 00:10:37.454
it the VIP table it's the
one that was next to you,

00:10:37.454 --> 00:10:38.120
with the turret.

00:10:38.120 --> 00:10:39.860
SPEAKER: I wasn't at the
VIP table last night?

