MARC DJOZLIJA:
You see cityscape.

00:10:50.604 --> 00:10:51.590
You see architecture.

00:10:51.590 --> 00:10:55.250
You see more than just
people walking around.

00:10:55.250 --> 00:10:57.110
And it's a totally
different dynamic.

