And it's just so beautiful
what that stretch of Woodward

00:11:08.810 --> 00:11:09.670
has become.

00:11:09.670 --> 00:11:12.260
And with the Shinola Hotel
going up a couple doors

00:11:12.260 --> 00:11:14.180
away from you, you made
the right decision.

00:11:14.180 --> 00:11:16.596
MARC DJOZLIJA: Well, they said
all the commerce around us,

00:11:16.596 --> 00:11:19.170
the Element Hotel will be right
behind us, the Siren Hotel,

00:11:19.170 --> 00:11:21.140
will be right next to them.

00:11:21.140 --> 00:11:24.500
So when we talked about
timing and location,

00:11:24.500 --> 00:11:26.280
it just worked out
amazing for us.

