But at the time, we
totally speculated

00:11:28.250 --> 00:11:30.110
that, if we were
close to the arenas

00:11:30.110 --> 00:11:32.240
and we were close to the
event spaces, that maybe

00:11:32.240 --> 00:11:34.730
we could draw some
traffic to the area.

00:11:34.730 --> 00:11:36.909
And no matter how
quirky the space was--

00:11:36.909 --> 00:11:38.700
but like I said, it
get's better every day.

00:11:38.700 --> 00:11:41.280
