really helped us, as well,

00:11:41.280 --> 00:11:45.140
because of the fact that, when
you talk about 20,000 people

00:11:45.140 --> 00:11:49.880
coming down on a
Wednesday in wintertime,

00:11:49.880 --> 00:11:51.980
