the Masonic Temple

00:12:37.790 --> 00:12:39.350
in what was the old Chinatown.

00:12:39.350 --> 00:12:41.780
So the building right
across the street from us,

00:12:41.780 --> 00:12:44.180
Chung's, was the last
Chinese restaurant

00:12:44.180 --> 00:12:47.060
that was still open in
the old Chinatown in 2000.

