And a gentlemen we partnered
with found this facility,

00:12:49.792 --> 00:12:51.500
wanted to rehab the
building, and thought

00:12:51.500 --> 00:12:53.895
it'd be cool to open
a Chinese restaurant

00:12:53.895 --> 00:12:54.770
in the old Chinatown.

00:12:54.770 --> 00:12:57.820
So we opened a place called The
Peterboro about two years ago.

00:12:57.820 --> 00:13:00.300
And so we also have that
on the other side of us

00:13:00.300 --> 00:13:03.900
that also is perfectly
located for the new arena.

00:13:03.900 --> 00:13:06.440
And Founders Brewery just opened
across the street from us,

00:13:06.440 --> 00:13:08.660
now, which will also
bring people to the area.

00:13:08.660 --> 00:13:11.000
We're bridging the
gap between the arena

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:13.740
and what is quote,
unquote, "Midtown,"

00:13:13.740 --> 00:13:15.620
on the other side of
Martin Luther King,

00:13:15.620 --> 00:13:17.480
where it was kind of
the Cass corridor.

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:19.530
But the shipping
container facility,

00:13:19.530 --> 00:13:21.404
