00:13:21.404 --> 00:13:22.500
is right next to us.

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:23.850
So that's being built, as well.

00:13:23.850 --> 00:13:25.730
So we're going to be
right smack, hopefully,

00:13:25.730 --> 00:13:28.124
again in an emerging
area of Detroit,

00:13:28.124 --> 00:13:30.040
where all the commerce
will come up around us.

00:13:30.040 --> 00:13:32.491
And we will just hopefully
position ourself properly,

00:13:32.491 --> 00:13:32.990
again.

00:13:32.990 --> 00:13:33.740
SPEAKER: It's such
an exciting time.

